This directory contains compiled WebAssembly derivatives of third-party tree-sitter grammars.
Both are MIT-licensed; their notices are reproduced below per the "included in all copies or
substantial portions" requirement. See checksums.json for exact provenance (source package,
version, build tool) of each .wasm file.

